- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses the state complexity of the distinguishability operation. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper uses Boolean operators in its generalization of the distinguishability operation. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses the iteration of the distinguishability operation and its fixed point. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper provides an upper bound for the state complexity of the distinguishability operation.
